           SPELL=smgl-upstart
         VERSION=0.2
        WEB_SITE=http://www.sourcemage.org
         ENTERED=20090907
      LICENSE[0]=GPL
           SHORT="SMGL upstart scripts"
cat << EOF
Upstart is a replacement for the /sbin/init daemon which handles starting of
tasks and services during boot, stopping them during shutdown and
supervising them while the system is running.

This spell provides a set of native upstart init scripts to boot your box.
EOF
